<li>Sr Dev's Review of The Odin Project: <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=gjPSVNVelro">Part 1</a> &amp; <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=jToxebcZNvA">Part 2</a>;</li>
